custom-machine-setup-824.md:During machine [enlistment](/t/add-nodes/821#heading--enlistment), [deployment](/t/deploy-nodes/825), [commissioning](/t/commission-nodes/822) and machine installation, MAAS sends [Tempita-derived](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ravenac95/tempita/master/docs/index.txt) configuration files to the [cloud-init](https://launchpad.net/cloud-init) process running on the target machine. MAAS refers to this process as **preseeding**.These preseed files are used to configure a machine's ephemeral and installation environments and can be modified or augmented to a custom machine configuration.
