disk-erasure-774.md:Disk erasure pertains to the erasing of data on each of a machine's disks when the machine has been released (see [Release action](/t/concepts-and-terms/785#heading--release)) back into the pool of available machines. The user can choose from among three erasure types before confirming the Release action. A default erasure configuration can also be set.
