high-availability-804.md:If you are enabling DHCP for the first time after adding a second rack controller, please read [Enabling DHCP](/t/dhcp/759#heading--enabling-dhcp).  On the other hand, if you have already enabled DHCP on your initial rack controller, you'll need to reconfigure DHCP.
