select-and-import-images-751.md:You can tell MAAS to sync images hourly, at the region level, using a toggle switch in the top-right corner of the screen.  See [Boot image sources](/t/images/754#boot-image-sources)) for more details. We highly recommended synching images hourly. Syncing at the rack controller level (from regiond) occurs every 5 min and cannot be disabled.
